//"Welcome to the Labri Market! You can find anything here." -- Basler
You grew up in a highly populated center of trade and culture. You're familiar with art, commerce, and political power. You've seen people from all over, and have heard or can even speak multiple languages.
You've learned to approach situations via negotiation.

